      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1914_AS_RBH_1_00022"/>Hrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr Richard</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Beer Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb34344">Weissenbach</rs>.</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Am <rs ref="#pmb236" type="place">Attersee</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb519"><hi rend="latintype">Ober Oesterreich</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1914_AS_RBH_1_00021"/><hi rend="pre-print"><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="T_L02189-1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb1138">Cresta Palace, Celerina</rs><note type="textConst" corresp="T_L02189-1">von Schnitzler unterstrichen</note></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1914_AS_RBH_1_00022"/><date when="1914-08-02">2. 8. 914</date>. Wir<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind – u bleiben vorläufig hier –
               (Bahnverkehr in der <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43435">Schweiz</rs> nur für Militär
               zulä<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ig; –) la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Sie uns wi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en wie es Ihnen geht; – hier wär es wundervoll – we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> man ruhiger <pb facs="1914_AS_RBH_1_00021"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein
               könnte. Das <rs ref="#pmb1061" type="place">Engadin</rs> wie ausge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>torben. Hier im
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb1138">Hotel</rs> kaum noch 20 Gä<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te.</p><closer>Wir grüßen herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t.<lb/>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
